It's WHICH WAS WORSE season but this time it's an MCU TV Edition! Four years ago, two shows made their debut as parts of the Marvel Cinematic Universe and were so UNIVERSALLY panned we may NEVER see them again. What else could we be talking about besides INHUMANS and IRON FIST?! With these undeniable flops on our hands join The Don and Dan The Comic Book Man as they argue about WHICH WAS WORSE! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! Please [SUPPORT US ON PATREON](http://Patreon.com/CBCClubhouse)!

